Sea, saying that such claim undermined the spirit of the Madrid
communique signed between the two countries last month.
</P>
<P>
Yilmaz reportedly said in the Sunday edition of the U.S. daily
Washington Post that international law could not be applied in
the Aegean Sea.
</P>
