<HEADLINE> Japan to Send 320 Members to Nagano Winter Olympics </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, August 6 (Xinhua) -- Japan will send 320 athletes and
officials to the Nagano Olympic Winter Games in February next
year, the Japanese Olympic Committee (JOC) said Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
