<HEADLINE> Sino-German Afforestation Project in Central China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHANGSHA, August 6 (Xinhua) -- A five-year Sino-German
afforestation project is planned for central China's Hunan
Province.
</P>
<P>
It will cover a 30,000-ha area, and includes three sections
around Dongting Lake in Yueyang City.
</P>
<P>
The project has got 94.35 million yuan worth of German bank
loans.
</P>
<P>
