<HEADLINE> Costa Rica Pushes On With High-Tech Zone </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SAN JOSE, August 5 (Xinhua) -- Costa Rica has outlined its
plans to push forward the high-tech industrial zone in its central
region by attracting more foreign investment.
